以下是一段适用于年终总结的英文描述，强调你着眼大局、总结经验、推动改进与标准化的能力：


---

"Took a big-picture view to reflect on project outcomes, identified areas for improvement, and incorporated lessons learned into future testing strategies. Proactively contributed to the refinement of testing processes and helped establish best practices and standards to enhance team efficiency and reliability for upcoming cloud-based projects."


---

你也可以加一句强调你推动知识共享或文档化，例如：

"Documented key findings and shared them across teams to promote alignment and continuous improvement."

是否还需要结合具体工作内容进一步定制？

